There is nothing better than homemade Gin Fizz, the mixture of the best gin cocktail using locally produced artisanal gin for a spirit that offers up fruity flavours unique to African wild botanicals. Ingredients 45 ml Woodstock gin 15 ml Lime juice 35 ml Cane syrup Strawberries Cucumber Slice of lime Splash of soda water Method In a highball glass, add gin with fresh lime juice. Add the cane syrup for sweetness, throw in the strawberries and cucumbers and blend. To top it off, add your slice of lime and tonic water to really make your drink fizz.